<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 09 at 6:16AM EST  by NWS Cleveland</headline>
<description>...BRIEF PERIOD OF SNOW EARLY THIS MORNING...
A brief period of snow will quickly transition over to rain early
this morning. A quick inch or two of snow will be possible which
will result in some slick spots on roadways. Gusty southeast winds
could result in reduced visibilities.</description>
